Subscribe to Vision Video for more faith-based movies and tv series: https://bit.ly/3LrbGIN

After Samuel delivers a message from heaven to Saul about wiping out Amalek in the south, King Saul leads a military campaign against the evil kingdom. Saul returns with his troops triumphantly and announces a big special event to celebrate the victory. Samuel arrives to confront Saul; the king has blatantly ignored the most important part of heavens instruction. 

Saul knows what he has done and left undone, but doesnt want to acknowledge his mistakes let alone his resentment toward Samuel and Gods message. The 2 men clash badly and fall out for good. It is the beginning of the end of Sauls kingship (and life).

Billy Angel tells the Biblical story like you've never heard it before.
